description:
That's right. The builders of these stunning brand-new homes have given us clear instructions, " They HAVE to be sold"

1 Sawmill Place demands street presence, offering an unparalleled facade & beautiful presentation from the moment you enter the home.

Upon entering the home, you will be immediately impressed by the 2.7m high ceilings & floating staircase, the functional floorplan, and the quality of the residence. Continuing through, you will arrive at the open-plan sleek kitchen offering a walk-in pantry & panoramic views of the meals and living area, and through to the outdoor alfresco. With a north-easterly aspect, the outdoor entertaining area is sundrenched for most hours of the day and has plenty of room to host your next barbeque or backyard cricket match.

Offering four spacious bedrooms upstairs, each with built-in wardrobes, and the master bedroom offers a sizeable walk-in robe and ensuite, boasting floor-to-ceiling tiles and contains a much sought-after fifth bedroom on the lower floor for in-law or guest accommodation. This home is surrounded by other quality-built homes, fantastic schools and is central to shopping complexes, transport, parks, and recreational facilities, the location is the cherry on top of this divine opportunity.

- 5 Bed | 2 Bath | 2 Car | 450m2 Block
- Ducted air-conditioning with ceiling fans to each room
- Timber flooring & downlights throughout
- Private balcony to 4th bedroom
- 400m to Macquarie Street Bus Stop
- 700m to Church Street Reserve
- 3 mins to Bligh Park Hotel
- Windsor South Public School & Windsor High School Catchment

With two beautiful homes to choose from offering a turn key opportunity, they're ready for their new owners. DON'T MISS OUT - THESE HOMES WILL AND MUST BE SOLD

Contact Daniel Llamas on 0421 908 736 or d.llamas@raywhite.com to lock in an inspection or for further information.
